nodes.text: Swim Meet is a mini adventure for use in the Rise of the Empire era, published on the Wizards of the Coast website. It was written by Jeff Quick and published on August 22, 2002.
Set on Lobaoc during the Rise of the Empire era, the heroes must chase down a dark Mon Calamari Jedi.
"Swim Meet" is intended for four player characters of 12th level.
